	•	Normal Mode:-
	•	When a button is pressed (BTN_DOORx), that door’s relay energizes and LED turns ON.
	•	After 5 seconds, the door locks again.
	•	Interlock Mode:-
	•	DIP switches control which doors can open together.
	•	Example: DIP1 ON means Door1 won’t open if any other door is already open.
	•	Emergency Override:-
	•	When EMERGENCY is triggered, all doors lock and buzzer sounds for 5 seconds.
